metadata.name: state_of_blue
metadata.description:
this is underscore's state_of_blue

underscore_2 is a collection of 25 1/1 hand-drawn animated pieces focusing on sorrow, sadness, isolation, calmness, tranquility, loyalty, and royalty. all that is blue. reaching deep into the abyss to discover things usually left untouched. this is _xo's introduction to the state of blue
